Reasoning: 
- cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) is the most likely category as the paper analyzes the social network structure among Tumblr users and their behavior.
- cs.SOC (Social and Behavioral Sciences) is also likely as the paper compares Tumblr with other social media networks and discusses its hybrid characteristics.
- cs.IR (Information Retrieval) is another possible category as the paper analyzes user-generated content on Tumblr.
- cs.MM (Multimedia) is a possible category as the paper mentions the rich content on Tumblr.
- cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction) is also a possible category as the paper discusses user behavior and reblogging patterns.
